"半澤單車","source_url":"https://www.facebook.com/bcbikehk/posts/159753212127005","tags":"口罩","language":"zh"}},{"node":{"title":"自制酒精搓手液","text":"近日「酒精搓手液」斷晒市，雖然清潔雙手其實最好用清水及肥皂沖洗，不過於街上想用消毒搓手液又不能太吝嗇，需要用 20-30 秒均勻覆蓋全手表面，可惜就算買到都十幾廿蚊一樽仔，用兩用就冇曬。","date":"2020-01-28","image_url":"https://i.imgur.com/2vTQXPO.jpg","source_description":"生死教育 X 伍桂麟","source_url":"https://www.facebook.com/LifeAndDeathEducation/photos/a.703005379797822/2562090527222622","tags":"醫學知識","language":"zh"}},{"node":{"title":"冠狀病毒是甚麼？","text":"在近期海量的消息之中，相信大家不會對「冠狀病毒」四隻字感到陌生。但究竟冠狀病毒是甚麼？筆者想借本文，向各位讀者作簡單介紹。","date":"2020-01-28","image_url":"https://i.imgur.com/apxBpk9.png","source_description":"hkmedwords.furious","source_url":"https://www.instagram.com/p/B72m4wfh3JS/","tags":"醫學知識","language":"zh"}},{"node":{"title":"2019-nCoV 武漢肺炎疫情及公共衛生短訊 (廣東話 Cantonese)","text":"","date":"2020-01-28","image_url":"http://i3.ytimg.com/vi/DKOqOB3-HSo/maxresdefault.jpg","source_description":"Jon Chui","source_url":"https://youtu.be/DKOqOB3-HSo","tags":"醫學知識","language":"zh"}},{"node":{"title":"口罩唔肚餓，食飯咪戴囉！","text":"用餐時，如將口罩拉到下巴進食，會將口罩外的污物「食晒落肚」，故用餐時應直接脫掉口罩。","date":"2020-01-26","image_url":"https://i.imgur.com/ns40BYQ.png","source_description":"何栢良醫生","source_url":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCe1Ur94rhCO4KKyAn7BykuA","tags":"口罩","language":"zh"}},{"node":{"title":"[2019-nCoV 更新]隻病毒係識得人傳人","text":"昨日醫學期刊《刺針》出咗一堆關於 2019-nCoV 嘅文獻，現擇錄兩篇嘅重點，供大家了解。","date":"2020-01-25","image_url":"https://i.imgur.com/uzdXM0Y.jpg","source_description":"醫言 · 憤怒","source_url":"https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=180057286711950&id=109420420442304","tags":"醫學知識","language":"zh"}},{"node":{"title":"如何減低武漢肺炎患病風險？","text":"我們可以如何自保呢？沙士爆發以後，很多針對冠狀病毒的研究都異口同聲指出使用醫用口罩和保持雙手清潔是減低染病風險的重要元素。","date":"2020-01-21","image_url":"https://stem.ust.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/iStock-1139022663.jpg","source_description":"STEM@HKUST","source_url":"https://stem.ust.hk/zh/%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e6%b8%9b%e4%bd%8e%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e6%82%a3%e7%97%85%e9%a2%a8%e9%9a%aa/","tags":"醫學知識","language":"zh"}},{"node":{"title":"不明「不明原因的肺炎」","text":"不明「不明原因的肺炎」","date":"2020-01-16","image_url":"https://static.hkej.net/hkej/images/2020/01/16/2354673_f67988dede7994fbd0422046c238541c_620.jpg","source_description":"信健康","source_url":"https://health.hkej.com/health/article?suid=2354673&subjectline=%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E7%9A%84%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%8D","tags":"實用網站","language":"zh"}},{"node":{"title":"【消毒陷阱】小心產品無助消毒反致敏，17款通過安全測試的濕紙巾和搓手液。","text":"港人衞生意識日增，越來越多人使用濕紙巾及搓手液清潔及消毒。然而濕紙巾不僅因不能分解而產生環保問題，有關產品或含致敏成分，容易導致皮膚敏感甚至皮膚炎，外國便有不少兒童因此感到不適，反映當中存在安全隱患。","date":"2019-05-18","image_url":"https://medicalinspire.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wetwipesCOV.jpg","source_description":"Medical Inspire 醫．思維","source_url":"https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/34582","tags":"醫學知識","language":"zh"}},{"node":{"title":"測試29款口罩 3款過濾細菌效率高於99.9%","text":"消費者委員會從市面搜集了29款口罩進行測試，發現某些型號品質較為遜色。另邀請了多位醫護專家講解使用外科口罩應注意的事項。","date":"2017-12-01","image_url":"https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/f/article/2256/1488c836/494_surgical-masks.jpg","source_description":"選擇月刊 @ 消費者委員會","source_url":"https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/f/article/2256/494_p14-21a.pdf","tags":"口罩","language":"zh"}},{"node":{"title":"護士哥哥教你正確洗手程序 -《拉姑娘醫院日常》","text":"","date":"2017-09-01","image_url":"https://i.imgur.com/gAMHDW0.png","source_description":"拉哥 Lai UP","source_url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CiXaGNXEQEo","tags":"醫學知識","language":"zh"}}]}},"pageContext":{"locale":"zh"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1271460761","2227081814","770724894"]}